description: The status of the document in the process. Possible values are - RECE (Received) - DRFT (Drafted) - PENA (Pending Approval) - PENU (Pending Update) - PENC (Pending Confirmation) - CONF (Confirmed) - REJE (Rejected) - APPR (Approved) - ISSU (Issued) - SURR (Surrendered) - SUBM (Submitted) - VOID (Void) - REQS (Requested) - CMPL (Completed) - HOLD (On Hold) - RELS (Released) - CANC (Cancelled) More details can be found on GitHub
